  <div class="container about-section">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <p class="mission-statement">
          Welcome to AgriSustain, your go-to platform for sustainable agriculture, community engagement, and healthy living. <br />
          Our application is designed to empower farmers and consumers alike with a wealth of resources and tools aimed
          at promoting responsible farming practices and fostering a thriving agricultural community.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <h3 class="text-center section-subheading">Our Mission</h3>
        <p class="mission-statement">
          At AgriSustain, we are on a mission to revolutionize agriculture by providing comprehensive solutions that bridge
          the gap between farmers and consumers. Our platform is committed to promoting sustainable farming practices,
          fostering community engagement, and ensuring the availability of fresh, locally grown produce.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <h3 class="text-center section-subheading">Key Features</h3>
        <ul class="key-features">
          <li class="key-feature">
            <h3>Crop Information and Tracking:</h3>
            <p>
              Access detailed information on various crops, including growth patterns, optimal conditions, and harvesting
              techniques. Utilize our crop tracking tools to monitor and manage your crops effectively.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="key-feature">
            <h3>Farmers Hub:</h3>
            <p>
              A centralized hub offering a wealth of information on agricultural best practices. Connect with fellow farmers,
              share experiences, and stay updated on the latest trends in agriculture.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="key-feature">
            <h3>Community Gardens:</h3>
            <p>
              Engage in community farming groups with our dedicated garden management resources. Learn how to start and manage
              community gardens, fostering a sense of unity and sustainability.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="key-feature">
            <h3>Nutrition Information and Recipes:</h3>
            <p>
              Explore a rich repository of nutrition information related to locally grown produce. Discover delicious recipes that
              make the most of sustainably farmed ingredients.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="key-feature">
            <h3>Marketplace:</h3>
            <p>
              A platform that connects farmers directly with consumers. Purchase fresh, locally grown produce directly from
              farmers, promoting a sustainable and supportive marketplace.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="key-feature">
            <h3>Weather Information:</h3>
            <p>
              Stay informed with real-time weather updates relevant to your farming activities. Plan your agricultural activities
              effectively based on accurate weather forecasts.
            </p>
          </li>
